strings: <voice_0x01001324><se_def>Black and white: Wait for me, there's so much more...
<voice_0x01001326><se_def>Black and white: Miss you! Help, good people!
<voice_0x01001327><se_def>Black and white: Why do you see me in this state?
<voice_0x01001329>He's not alone, he smells like smart blood. of blood
<voice_0x0100132A>There has to be another... Hakeem's ultimate successor must be found.
<voice_0x0100132B><se_def>Black and white: Send a message? What can I say! What does "chosen follower" mean?
<voice_0x0100132C><se_def>Black and white: I don't understand whether this is wrong...
